ZOOKEEPER SERVICE LAYER 
=======================

Provides servlet/spring based abstraction for leader election and presence in Zookeeper

- assumes spring/servlet presence
- import applicationContext-zookeeper-all.xml or custom selection of sub-contexts per feature
- zookeeper paths are determined by the servlet display name in web.xml
- provides some basic MBeans for leader election and zookeeper client



Basic maven projet with spring

1. Checkout the code using git clone
2. Import Existing Maven Project in Eclipse
3. Build the projects using mvn install eclipse:eclipse from the command line
